data.description: Town of Big Flats, getaway Cabin situated on 8 gorgeous acres of towering pines and located on the ATV / snowmobile trail. What more could you ask for? Newly refreshed and move in ready with 2 bedrooms, 1 full bath, and an open concept kitchen and living room area, Deck and two large storage shed/garages will easily store all the toys. Spend your weekends relaxing in the heart of Adams County enjoying peace & quiet along with the plentiful wildlife!
